title: Is Lunchbox Leaving The Show?

description:
Lunchbox tells the show about a serious job offer, Lady Antebellum stops by the studio, NFL player Matt Overton sings his favorite Jason Aldean song, Arkansas Keith calls the show and Bobby gets ready for his role on the ACM Awards!
